    .col-lg-2.col-lg-offset-0.col-xs-4.col-xs-offset-4
      button.material-button.material-button-raised.material-theme-red.full-width(rcs-go-home) 管理餐厅
    .col-lg-2.col-lg-offset-0.col-xs-4.col-xs-offset-4
      button.material-button.material-button-raised.material-theme-red.full-width(ng-if="isManager()" rcs-go-admin) 分配管理员
